Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

; Windows clamps gamma ramps to a narrow range around identity to stop
; malware from blanking the screen. This key (the same one f.lux uses)
; unlocks the full range so strong temperature/brightness settings work.
; Import as administrator, then reboot or re-login.

[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\ICM]
"GdiIcmGammaRange"=dword:00000100
